<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٦٩١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6272">مُعَلَّى بْنُ أَسَدٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6858">وُهَيْبٌ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3721">ابْنِ طَاوُسٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2980">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span>،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">«احْتَجَمَ وَأَعْطَى الْحَجَّامَ أَجْرَهُ وَاسْتَعَطَ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>